Name: Fruit Girl Kiss
About the game: This is a casual strategy game of 'Fruit + Lianliankan + Beautiful Girl'. The player's goal is to eliminate the fruits of each level within a fixed time in order to pass the level. Connect two identical fruits by clicking to eliminate them. Every time you clear a chapter in this game, you can unlock the corresponding CG image in the gallery.
